# S05-T01: Tablet Layout

## Objective
Define tablet-first responsive AppShell layout optimized for landscape orientation, target resolutions per UI_REGULATION.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Breakpoints (Tailwind): `sm`(640), `md`(1024 iPad), `lg`(1366), `xl`(1920).
- Default orientation: landscape; portrait shows "ROTATE DEVICE" notice.
- Safe-area insets respected (`env(safe-area-inset-*)`).
- Top/Center/Bottom layout per UI_REGULATION section 3.
- Verified on: 1920×1080, 1366×768, 1280×800, iPad landscape.

## Steps
1. Update `AppShell` (from S01-T10) grid template.
2. Add orientation lock notice component.
3. Wire safe-area CSS variables.
4. Add manual viewport snapshots (deferred to S07).

## Invariants
- Video container always center, never <60% width on tablet+.
- HUD slots never overlap video center 10%.
- No horizontal scroll at any supported resolution.
